---
title: Slow-Cooked Chicken & Double Bacon Casserole  with Potato Mash & Veggies
description: We love a slow-cooked meal! There’s something magic about being able to throw a bunch of ingredients into a pot, and come
home later to a fully-formed meal. These chicken drumsticks will be falling apart by the time you’re ready to eat, in a rich
tomato-based sauce with tender veggies and salty, savoury bacon. Pile it onto creamy mash and enjoy this warm and cosy meal.
